appropriations: This measure has been amended to remove the appropriation from the University of Hawaii Conference Center Revolving Fund that was included in the previous version of the bill. As a result, this final version does not contain any appropriation. All expenditures will be made directly from the revolving fund as revenues are collected.
updates_from_previous_fiscal_note: This fiscal note pertains to H.B. 1169, C.D. 1, which differs from the previous version, S.D. 2. The primary substantive change made by the conference committee was the removal of an appropriation from the University of Hawaii Conference Center Revolving Fund. The final version of the bill establishes the fund and transfers existing balances but no longer appropriates funds for expenditures.
